title: (Tues Full Show) International Women’s Day with Hailey Whitters and Tenille Townes + Lunchbox Tries to Buy Jon Bon Jovi’s House + Raymundo Offered to Stay at Someone’s House in Florida
itunes:title: (Tues Full Show) International Women’s Day with Hailey Whitters and Tenille Townes + Lunchbox Tries to Buy Jon Bon Jovi’s House + Raymundo Offered to Stay at Someone’s House in Florida
description:
We celebrate International Women’s Day by bringing in two of our favorite new female artists to perform, Hailey Whitters and Tenille Townes. Lunchbox calls to try and buy Jon Bon Jovi’s house that’s for sale using his own lyrics. Raymundo reveals a listener has invited him to stay in his ‘mansion’ for the Strawberry Festival in Florida.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
